{"id":228,"parent_id":224,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":228,"title":"Hebrews 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Heb.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","The gospel was offered to ancient Israel—Saints enter into the rest of the Lord—Though tempted in all points, Jesus was without sin."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.1","order":"03.21.004.23574"},["b","1"],"Let us therefore fear, lest, a promise being left",["i","us"],"of entering into his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"rest"],", any of you should seem to come short of it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.2","order":"03.21.004.23575"},["b","2"],"For unto us was the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"gospel"],"preached, as well as unto them: but the word preached did not profit them, not being mixed with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"faith"],"in them that heard",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.3","order":"03.21.004.23576"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"For"],"we which have believed do enter into rest, as he said, As I have sworn in my wrath, if they shall enter into my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"rest"],": although the works were finished from the foundation of the world."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.4","order":"03.21.004.23577"},["b","4"],"For he spake in a certain place of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"seventh",["i","day"]],"on this wise, And God did rest the seventh day from all his works."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.5","order":"03.21.004.23578"},["b","5"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"And"],"in this",["i","place"],"again, If they shall enter into my rest."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.6","order":"03.21.004.23579"},["b","6"],"Seeing therefore it remaineth that some must enter therein, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"they"],"to whom it was first preached entered not in because of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"unbelief"],":"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.7","order":"03.21.004.23580"},["b","7"],"Again, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"limiteth"],"a certain day, saying in David, To day, after so long a time; as it is said, To day if ye will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"hear"],"his voice,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"harden"],"not your hearts."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.8","order":"03.21.004.23581"},["b","8"],"For if",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Jesus"],"had given them rest, then would he not afterward have spoken of another day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.9","order":"03.21.004.23582"},["b","9"],"There remaineth therefore a rest to the people of God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.10","order":"03.21.004.23583"},["b","10"],"For he that is entered into his rest, he also hath ceased from his own works, as God",["i","did"],"from his."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.11","order":"03.21.004.23584"},["b","11"],"Let us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"labour"],"therefore to enter into that rest, lest any man fall after the same example of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12","order":"03.21.004.23585"},["b","12"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"word"],"of God",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"quick"],", and powerful, and sharper than any twoedged",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"sword"],",",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"piercing"],"even to the dividing asunder of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_12e"},"soul"],"and spirit, and of the joints and marrow, and",["i","is"],"a",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_12f"},"discerner"],"of the",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_12g"},"thoughts"],"and",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_12h"},"intents"],"of the heart."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.13","order":"03.21.004.23586"},["b","13"],"Neither is there any creature that is not manifest in his sight: but all things",["i","are"],"naked and opened unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"eyes"],"of him with whom we have to do."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.14","order":"03.21.004.23587"},["b","14"],"Seeing then that we have a great high priest, that is passed into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"heavens"],", Jesus the Son of God, let us hold fast",["i","our"],"profession."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.15","order":"03.21.004.23588"},["b","15"],"For we have not an high priest",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"which"],"cannot be touched with the feeling of our infirmities; but was in all points",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"tempted"],"like as",["i","we are, yet"],"without",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.16","order":"03.21.004.23589"},["b","16"],"Let us therefore come boldly unto the throne of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"grace"],", that we may obtain mercy, and find grace to help in time of need."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.1a","order":"03.21.004.23590"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-glory-of"},"TG God, Glory of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rest"},"Rest"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.2a","order":"03.21.004.23592"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.2b","order":"03.21.004.23594"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.3a","order":"03.21.004.23596"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-heb/4.3"},["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 4:3 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.3b","order":"03.21.004.23598"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.9"},"D&C 19:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.4a","order":"03.21.004.23600"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.5a","order":"03.21.004.23602"},["b","5a"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 4:5 And in this place again, If they",["i","harden not their hearts they"],"shall enter into my rest."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.6a","order":"03.21.004.23604"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"those who formerly were taught the gospel."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.6b","order":"03.21.004.23606"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"disobedience, unbelief, obstinacy."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.7a","order":"03.21.004.23608"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"appoints, decrees, constitutes."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.7b","order":"03.21.004.23610"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/95.7"},"Ps. 95:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.7c","order":"03.21.004.23612"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.8a","order":"03.21.004.23614"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/17.9"},"Ex. 17:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.45"},"Acts 7:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.11a","order":"03.21.004.23616"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"hasten, be eager."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.11b","order":"03.21.004.23618"},["b","11b"],["span.small","GR"],"obstinacy, disobedience.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12a","order":"03.21.004.23620"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.5"},"Alma 31:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.2"},"D&C 6:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.2"},"11:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.2"},"12:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.2"},"14:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.1"},"33:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12b","order":"03.21.004.23622"},["b","12b"],["span.small","GR"],"living."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12c","order":"03.21.004.23624"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.2"},"Isa. 49:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.12.12-17"},"Rev. 2:12 (12–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12d","order":"03.21.004.23626"},["b","12d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/6.5"},"Hosea 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.6"},"D&C 85:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"12e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12e","order":"03.21.004.23628"},["b","12e"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 4:12 …",["i","body"],"…"],["div",{"id":"12f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12f","order":"03.21.004.23630"},["b","12f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/14.25.24-25"},"1 Cor. 14:25 (24–25)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12g","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12g","order":"03.21.004.23632"},["b","12g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.16"},"D&C 6:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"12h","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12h","order":"03.21.004.23634"},["b","12h"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/motivations"},"TG Motivations"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.13a","order":"03.21.004.23636"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/5.21"},"Prov. 5:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.14a","order":"03.21.004.23638"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.24"},"Heb. 9:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.15a","order":"03.21.004.23640"},["b","15a"],["span.small","GR"],"unable to sympathize with our frailties, imperfections."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.15b","order":"03.21.004.23642"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-temptation-of"},"Jesus Christ, Temptation of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temptation"},"Temptation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.15c","order":"03.21.004.23644"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.46"},"John 8:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.26"},"Heb. 7:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.4"},"D&C 45:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.16a","order":"03.21.004.23646"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."]]}
